{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a rent cap of \u00a3250 PCM per bedroom.",
        "additional_details": "Many working people with low income, spend sometime more than half of their salary on rent. It is just not fair. Our basic right for affordable housing should come before the right to make more money.",
        "background": "Put a cap on private renting of \u00a3250 per bedroom per calendar month (PCM) so that it is affordable for people in the private rental sector. For example; one bedroom apartment 250\u00a3 PCM, two bedroom apartment 500\u00a3 PCM, three bedroom apartment 750\u00a3 PCM and so on.",
